# HimRate — Kamal Secrets (common to all destinations)
# Evaluated as shell script by Kamal; values inherited от env or
# `.kamal/secrets.<destination>` файла (written by CI или локально).
#
# SECURITY: KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD должен быть DEDICATED fine-grained PAT
# с scope `read:packages` (и `write:packages` для локальных pushes). НЕ
# использовать personal `gh auth token` — mixing dev/deploy creds, нельзя
# rotate independently, over-scoped для git operations. См.
# docs/runbooks/kamal_local_deploy.md для генерации + ротации.
#
# Fail-fast strategy: validation происходит в CI `Validate required secrets`
# step (ci.yml) ПЕРЕД kamal invocation. Локально — `:?` в KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD
# explicit guard с понятным message (единственная переменная которую developers
# реально забывают exported). Остальные passthrough — если set в env (через
# secrets.<destination> file или local export), используется; если missing →
# kamal будет error чётко когда попробует substitute в deploy.yml references.
#
# Why no `:?` sweep для всех vars:
# Kamal sources secrets-common ДО secrets.<destination> в некоторых code paths.
# Strict `:?` на vars which secrets.<destination> только set — would fail before
# file sourced. Keep passthrough здесь — Kamal merges values из обоих sources.

KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD=${KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD:?must be exported locally — see docs/runbooks/kamal_local_deploy.md для dedicated PAT setup}
RAILS_MASTER_KEY=${RAILS_MASTER_KEY:-$(cat config/master.key 2>/dev/null)}
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=$POSTGRES_PASSWORD
DATABASE_URL=$DATABASE_URL
REDIS_URL=$REDIS_URL
JWT_SECRET=$JWT_SECRET
SECRET_KEY_BASE=$SECRET_KEY_BASE
TWITCH_CLIENT_ID=$TWITCH_CLIENT_ID
TWITCH_CLIENT_SECRET=$TWITCH_CLIENT_SECRET
TWITCH_REDIRECT_URI=$TWITCH_REDIRECT_URI
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=$GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=$GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=$GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI
ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_PRIMARY_KEY=$ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_PRIMARY_KEY
ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_DETERMINISTIC_KEY=$ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_DETERMINISTIC_KEY
ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_KEY_DERIVATION_SALT=$ACTIVE_RECORD_ENCRYPTION_KEY_DERIVATION_SALT
FLIPPER_UI_PASSWORD=$FLIPPER_UI_PASSWORD
FLIPPER_UI_USER=$FLIPPER_UI_USER
ALLOWED_EXTENSION_ID=$ALLOWED_EXTENSION_ID
TWITCH_WEBHOOK_SECRET=$TWITCH_WEBHOOK_SECRET
EVENTSUB_WEBHOOK_URL=$EVENTSUB_WEBHOOK_URL
